    <briefdescription>
<para>Reader-writer mutex using two regular mutexes + atomic counters. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Multiple readers can hold the lock concurrently; writers have exclusive access. When Backend = <ref refid="structNullMutexBackend" kindref="compound">NullMutexBackend</ref>, all operations compile away.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Backend</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Static policy class satisfying the <ref refid="structNullMutexBackend" kindref="compound">NullMutexBackend</ref> contract. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
